---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Navbar from "../components/Navbar.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
---

<Layout title="Terms of Service | ValidMVPs">
  <div class="flex flex-col min-h-screen bg-[#F6F7FF]">
    <Navbar />

    <main class="grow pt-40 pb-24">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6">
        <h1
          class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bricolage font-medium text-[#0D1B15] mb-12"
        >
          Terms of Service
        </h1>

        <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none text-[#595E5C] font-inter">
          <p class="mb-6">Last updated: April 20, 2026</p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#0D1B15] mt-10 mb-4">
            1. Agreement to Terms
          </h2>
          <p class="mb-6">
            By accessing or using our website, you agree to be bound by these
            terms. If you disagree with any part of the terms, then you may not
            access the service.
          </p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#0D1B15] mt-10 mb-4">
            2. Technical Services
          </h2>
          <p class="mb-6">
            ValidMVPs provides fast-execution development services, MVP
            construction, and technical strategy for founders and startups. Our
            services are intended to help validate business ideas through
            functional software. The final responsibility for the business model
            and market validation remains with the client.
          </p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#0D1B15] mt-10 mb-4">
            3. Accuracy of Data
          </h2>
          <p class="mb-6">
            You are responsible for the accuracy of the STL files and patient
            data provided to us. We are not liable for errors resulting from
            inaccurate or low-quality digital impressions.
          </p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#0D1B15] mt-10 mb-4">
            4. Intellectual Property
          </h2>
          <p class="mb-6">
            The website and its original content, features, and functionality
            are and will remain the exclusive property of ValidMVPs and its
            licensors.
          </p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#0D1B15] mt-10 mb-4">
            5. Limitation of Liability
          </h2>
          <p class="mb-6">
            In no event shall ValidMVPs be liable for any indirect, incidental,
            special, consequential or punitive damages, including without
            limitation, loss of profits, data, use, goodwill, or other
            intangible losses.
          </p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#0D1B15] mt-10 mb-4">
            6. Governing Law
          </h2>
          <p class="mb-6">
            These terms shall be governed and construed in accordance with the
            laws of Pakistan, without regard to its conflict of law provisions.
          </p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#0D1B15] mt-10 mb-4">
            7. Contact Us
          </h2>
          <p class="mb-6">
            If you have any questions about these terms, please contact us at
            ahmedzulfiqar.dev@gmail.com.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </main>

    <Footer />
  </div>
</Layout>
